# Strategy Memos

This folder contains long-form strategic thinking and design notes related to the ODNB and Big Loud Shirt platforms.

Use this space for:
- Market validation summaries
- Product roadmap drafts
- Positioning frameworks
- GTM strategy shifts
- Pricing model experiments
- Investor one-pagers or pitch prep

---

## Suggested File Naming

- `go_to_market_phases.md`
- `positioning_vs_bi_tools.md`
- `revenue_model_notes.md`
- `funding_roadmap.md`
- `family_office_use_case.md`

---

## Quick Tip

Use this folder as your async whiteboard when working with contributors.
